truly one of the best homemade CHOCOLATE CHIP COOKIES in the world🍪🍪🍪sure, i’m biased but these also have dozens of 5 star reviews on my blog so the crew agrees🤌🏻

they’re vegan-friendly (use coconut oil or vegan butter) and they’re gluten-free too. i usually add walnuts in them but jord ate them all with his trial mix (lol) so i used 3 types of chocolate instead🍫🔥

google “rachlmansfield walnut chocolate chip cookies” for the recipe!

#rachleats #glutenfree #veganrecipes #chocolatechipcookies #dairyfree #easyrecipes #feedfeed #wholefoods

node.text:
saved the best for last baby: LITTLE BITES FUDGE BROWNIES🍫👌🏻these are a 100 out of 10 in my book. the texture and flavor is on point and they’re truly the best mini brownies ever (…sure i am biased but really😉)

the link to these is in my bio!! thank you guys SO much for participating in #rachllittlebitesweek !! truly overwhelmed with how many of you baked with us all week long. beyond cool and inspiring for the theme weeks to come baby!!!

#rachleats #glutenfree #dairyfree #nutfree #wholefoods #feedfeed #brownies #easyrecipes

node.text:
day 4 and the last day of #rachllittlebitesweek is here!! MINI FUDGE BROWNIE BITES! crinkly tops with a fudgy brownie center🍫🍫🍫they’re gluten-free + nut-free and truly just DAMN GOOD!!🤌🏻👌🏻pop ‘em frozen or eat them fresh and if you’re feeling frisky have some milk to dip them in!

LINK TO RECIPE IS IN BIO + rachlmansfield.com/copycat-little-bites-brownie-bites-gluten-free/

#rachleats #glutenfree #feedfeed #wholefoods #nutfree #brownies

node.text:
LITTLE BITES CHOCOLATE CHIP MUFFINS!🍫best part? when you make them at home you’re not limited to just 4 in a serving😂we made these on our live today and it was so fun (saved to IGTV!) and this recipe is gluten-free, nut-free and can be vegan if you use flax egg and vegan butter or oil.

full recipe scoop is on my blog + link is in bio!!

any guesses for what flavor comes out tomorrow for #rachllittlebitesweek ?!👇🏻😉

#rachleats #entenmanns #glutenfree #dairyfree #easyrecipes #feedfeed #wholefoods

node.text:
okay little bites fam - MINI CHOCOLATE CHIP MUFFINS are here!!! #rachllittlebitesweek is all hot and bothered with these eppppic chocolate chip muffins guys. i am still salivating over them from when i baked approx 100 mini muffins to perfect them for you😂🍫

these are gluten-free and nut-free and you can use vegan butter to make them vegan friends. and tbh you can even use regular all purpose flour to make them not gf too. 

LINK TO RECIPE IS IN MY BIO + rachlmansfield.com/copycat-little-bites-chocolate-chip-muffins/

+ don’t forget to tag me and #rachllittlebitesweek when you make any little bites recipe from my blog this week and i’ll send every single person a cookbook (yes.. really!) it does need to be US only as of now but i’ll let you know if it changes. (form must be submitted by EOD 8/18 to receive book!)

#rachleats #glutenfree #entenmanns #dairyfree #nutfree #easyrecipes #chocolatechipmuffins #feedfeed
